  <brief_title>Effect of Intraoperative IV Ketamine on Postoperative Morphine Consumption During Intestinal Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Intraoperative IV Ketamine on Postoperative Morphine Consumption During Intestinal Surgery and Its Effect on Salivary Cortisol and Alpha Amylase Levels</official_title>
